{"tid":2080892,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【港區國安法】MSCI主席：對香港前景未感憂慮　全球投資者都需要香港","createTime":"2020-06-26T19:02:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T22:19:54.000Z","uid":4740,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7b95267f74ac84dcba20aac9f64a154cd9b2b396","tid":2080892,"uid":4740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T19:02:13.000Z","msg":"金融經濟 18:59 2020/06/24<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nE79pBR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnE79pBR.jpg&h=90e2bc79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ MSCI主席兼行政總裁Henry Fernandez接受《彭博》時指，對本港前景未感憂慮，更指選擇香港市場，出於數項「很強勁的因素（very strong factors）」<br />\n<br />\n內地擬在港訂立「港區國安法」，市場普遍認為本港政治不確定性有所增加。不過國際指數編製公司MSCI此際卻意外地將亞洲市場指數衍生品的授權，由新加坡轉至港交所  （00388） 。MSCI主席兼行政總裁Henry Fernandez接受《彭博》訪問時指，對本港前景未感憂慮，更指選擇香港市場，出於數項「很強勁的因素（very strong factors）」。<br />\n<br />\nFernandez表示，香港投資者群體龐大，除了中國內地，亦包括地區及國際投資者，且港股市場頗具深度，方便資金流動。他補充，本港有能力建立投資「生態系統」，連結香港、內地、台灣等大中華市場。<br />\n<br />\nFernandez形容，香港屬環球其中一個最大的結構性投資產品（Structured Product）市場，亦促使該行作此決定。<br />\n<br />\n針對香港目前狀況，他指在過去超過40年間，已多次聽過關於「香港將死（demise）」之言論，但最終香港每次都強韌應對，故看好香港作為國際金融中心的前景。他指不但國際投資者需要香港作為進入內地市場的關口，內地亦需要香港，皆因香港監管、交易等層面發展都較為成熟。"},{"pid":"234544075eaac8ae5cc3e567d13bf23c633662b8","tid":2080892,"uid":4740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T19:02:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2679132/【港區國安法】MSCI主席：對香港前景未感憂慮%E3%80%80全球投資者都需要香港\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2679132%2F%E3%80%90%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E3%80%91MSCI%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%EF%BC%9A%E5%B0%8D%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%89%8D%E6%99%AF%E6%9C%AA%E6%84%9F%E6%86%82%E6%85%AE%25E3%2580%2580%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%85%E9%83%BD%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h0VeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=8b8ecd90\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2679132/【港區國安法】MSCI主席：對香港前景未感憂慮%E3%80%80全球投資者都需要香港</a>"},{"pid":"47cae1ae1c4f7242c221aee6719c065c00932652","tid":2080892,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T19:17:58.000Z","msg":"收咗幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39dd42203a2e3fc138c2e13238a379cea07f4729","tid":2080892,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T19:29:35.000Z","msg":"Msci之前一早納入左人民幣"},{"pid":"971a46102e8fc4d0e33c51552bb816b209597891","tid":2080892,"uid":4740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39dd42203a2e3fc138c2e13238a379cea07f4729","tid":2080892,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T19:29:35.000Z","msg":"Msci之前一早納入左人民幣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T19:30:52.000Z","msg":"A股入EM Index<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"1d6f134ce90de4bf4036b92eaa62faedd1e22d54","tid":2080892,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T19:31:02.000Z","msg":"仲有澳門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85a96c62fa8b40abc9d870c99cf078bc90ffaf1","tid":2080892,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T19:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398eeaa4cac2fd49f148c561b1f99a176ec9af4a","tid":2080892,"uid":256127,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T19:37:46.000Z","msg":"都上左船唔通唔撐咩"},{"pid":"336e779fde0ac7aeba49a982d9eecd1ab0b58609","tid":2080892,"uid":4740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T19:41:31.000Z","msg":"MSCI會唔會加南韓入發達市場指數(World Index)？FTSE已經加咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"41df75eefb89150caffde629f6e263d291a59773","tid":2080892,"uid":4740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T19:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}